# ==========================================
# KYTHIA-VANGUARD - Environment Variables
# ==========================================
# GUIDE:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to .env (remove .example)
# 2. Fill in the API Key below if you have one.
# 3. KYTHIA-VANGUARD Pro will still run 100% safely even if all these fields are left blank

# ------------------------------------------
# 1. SHODAN API KEY
# ------------------------------------------
# FUNCTION: Enables advanced OSINT features to identify ports, 
#         vulnerabilities (CVE), and target server information directly from the Shodan database 
#         without having to scan the target directly (Passive Recon).
# HOW TO GET: Sign up and retrieve an API Key at https://account.shodan.io/ 
# IF EMPTY: KYTHIA-VANGUARD will bypass the Shodan OSINT module. Port scanning will still run normally using the tool’s built-in Nmap/Socket.
SHODAN_API_KEY=""

# ------------------------------------------
# 2. HAVE I BEEN PWNED (HIBP) API KEY
# ------------------------------------------
# FUNCTION: Used by the OSINT module to check whether the target company’s emails 
#         (e.g., admin@kenndeclouv.com) have ever been leaked 
#         in a hacker database (data breach) in the past.
# HOW TO OBTAIN: Purchase/register for an API Key at https://haveibeenpwned.com/API/Key
# IF EMPTY: KYTHIA-VANGUARD will skip the specific email breach checking feature. Other recon features will not be affected at all.
HIBP_API_KEY=""